DescDetail: <<
	Flake8 is a wrapper around these tools:

	PyFlakes
	pep8
	Ned Batchelder's McCabe script
	
	Flake8 runs all the tools by launching the single flake8 script. It
	displays the warnings in a per-file, merged output.
